# Memory

Promoted insights from past sessions. Read-only at session start; appended to by the reflection process.

---

## How this file works

- New entries are appended under a dated heading (`## YYYY-MM-DD`)
- Entries are short bullets describing decisions, debugging insights, project status changes, or workflow preferences
- The reflection script (`reflect.py`) reads recent session logs, identifies what's worth promoting, and appends here
- Manual edits are fine but discouraged -- the file is meant to grow organically

